    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "FLY ALONG THE BEAUTIFUL LAKE ERIE SHORE-ALWAYS OVER THE\nWATER-DETROIT-CLEVELAND—90 MINUTES\nDelightful\nSwift\nDETROIT-CUrVILINO\nDETROIT\nCLEVELAND\n90\nMINUTES\nFascinating\nSafe\nHeromacine\nREC U.S. PAT OFF\nAIR WAYS, INC.\nReservations for flights should be made as far in advance as possible\nIf in Detroit Phone:\nIf in Cleveland Phone:\nDETROIT STATIONS\nCLEVELAND STATION\nMemorial Park and the River.\nD \u0026 C Dock-Foot of 9th Street.\nPhone: Hickory 6954\nPhone: Main 5704\nDowntown Station-Foot of 1st St.\nPhone: Cadillac 5480\nUptown Office-2010 East 9th St.\nD \u0026 C Ticket Office: Main 3580\nPhone: Main 218",
      "\"REMARKABLE PERFORMANCE\"\nOF THE\nAeromarine Airways, Inc.\n150,380 Miles Flown in Absolute Safety\n10,700 Passengers Carried-Always Over the Water\nLUXURIOUS FLYING BOATS\nThe Aeromarine Eleven-Passenger Enclosed Cabin Flying Cruisers are the pride of the aviation\nworld to-day.\nNo conveyance of sea, land or air is more exquisitely furnished than this kind\nof air boat.\nA mahogany cabin trimmed with silk and with comfortable leather upholstered\nreclining chairs aids in giving a sense of quiet luxury within this white and gold air yacht.\nThe\nseating arrangements of the plane enable you at all'times to have a clear view of the beautiful\nscenery beneath.\nAEROMARINE AIRWAYS, INC. (Great Lakes Division)\nC. F. REDDEN, President\nThe Largest Aerial Transportation Company in the World Operating Flying Boats\nDetroit - Cleveland - New York - Atlantic City - Key West - Havana - Miami\nBimini - Nassau\n124. 125"
    ],
